    <solution><div><h3>Worked Solution</h3>

<p>
A number is <alert>even</alert> if it is divisible by 2 with no remainder.<br/>
A number is <alert>odd</alert> if it is not divisible by 2, meaning that when the number is divided by 2, the remainder is 1.
</p>

