  </row>
</tabular>
<p/>
<p><alert>Recall:</alert></p>
<ul>
  <li>A number is <alert>even</alert> if its last digit is 0, 2, 4, 6, or 8.</li>
  <li>A number is <alert>odd</alert> if its last digit is 1, 3, 5, 7, or 9.</li>
</ul></div></solution>
